  "title": "Manufacturing Engineer/Production Supervisor (MNC Semiconductor/12-hour shift/East Region)",
  "description": "<p>Responsibilities:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Lead line leaders and operators to achieve daily production targets, quality, productivity, and yield.</li>\n  <li>Conduct daily pass-down meetings and escalate any line issues.</li>\n  <li>Manage manpower, overtime, and consumables planning.</li>\n  <li>Ensure adherence to manufacturing and safety procedures.</li>\n  <li>Train and coach leaders and operators to enhance performance.</li>\n  <li>Implement improvements to minimize human errors.</li>\n  <li>Maintain discipline and good housekeeping in the production line.</li>\n  <li>Collaborate with departments on projects, evaluations, and preventive maintenance in the fab.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Requirements:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Diploma and above in Engineering or equivalents.</li>\n  <li>Minimum 2 years of working experience in a related industry.</li>\n  <li>Experience in high-tech, high-volume manufacturing environment is preferred.</li>\n  <li>Strong leadership and communication skills.</li>\n  <li>Willing to work 12-hour shifts (permanent day or night, as assigned).</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>______________________________________________________</strong></p>\n<p><strong>HOW TO APPLY :</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Interested candidates, please submit your resume by clicking on “Quick Apply” or contact win@hkmsvs.com for more details.</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Please provide following information in the resume for immediate processing</strong></p>\n<p><strong>1) Reasons for leaving current and/or last employment</strong></p>\n<p><strong>2) Last drawn and/or current salary</strong></p>\n<p><strong>3) Expected salary</strong></p>\n<p><strong>4) Date of availability and/or Notice Period</strong></p>\n<p><strong>All applications will be treated in strictest confidence and only shortlisted candidates will be notified</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Wee Wai Dan</strong></p>\n<p><strong>EA License No : 03C5391</strong></p>\n<p><strong>EA Reg No : R22109628</strong></p>",
